e & Open 24/7** — no tickets, no crowds.\n\n---\n\n### 5. 🌿 清晖园 (Qinghui Garden) — *The Hidden Gem*\n- **📍 Address**: Huagai Road, Daliang, Shunde (heart of old town)\n- **✨ Why?** A 400-year-old UNESCO-recognized Ming-Qing garden — intimate, historic, lush, and deeply romantic. The epitome of Lingnan elegance.\n- **⏰ Best Time**: Weekday mornings (avoid weekends); opens 8:00, closes 17:30.\n- **🎫 Tickets**: ¥15 (free for students & seniors; ID required).\n\n---\n\n💡 **Pro Tip**: All five locations are interconnected by bike lanes or <15-min drives. Consider renting shared e-bikes (Meituan/Hellobike) for a charming, eco-friendly date loop!\n\n© Generated for you — enjoy your special time in Shunde! 💞"}
